description: Urgent notice on the treatment of pneumonia of unknown cause - Wuhan
27 people with pneumonia of unknown cause reported to the WHO.
WHO confirmed that a novel coronavirus had been isolated from one person who was hospitalised. 41 cases confirmed.
62 new cases, 8 deaths. * Hubei reported 17 deaths, all in Wuhan.
70 new cases. (Changing number from 390 to 495 due to official number given by Hubei). * 6 new deaths.
Death of a doctor confirmed. * 46 new cases, 6 new deaths.
First confirmed case of Wuhan resident visiting Bangkok since Jan. 8th.
Second confirmed case at airport, person arrived from Wuhan. Transferred to Nonthaburi.
Third confirmed case at airport. (Imported - transferred to Nonthaburi)
One more case, wife of 4th case. Might have been locally transmitted, waiting for more info.
(Exact place not released) Chinese national that stayed at hospital between Jan. 10th - 15th tests positive, had contact with infected person from Wuhan.
First confirmed case in Guangdong of man that visited relatives in Wuhan.
6 more cases. * 4 more cases. One case added from previous update.
23 new cases. 4th city with 100+ cases outside Hubei.
First two confirmed cases of people that visited Wuhan.
Eight confirmed cases. 2 locally transmitted. * 4 more cases.
3 more cases. * 5 more cases.  * 2 more cases.
3 more cases, locally transmitted. * 9 more cases, 3 locally transmitted. * 5 more cases.
4 more cases. * First death and 8 more cases.
11 new cases. 2nd city with over a 100 cases outside Hubei. * 9 new cases.
Three cases confirmed. Transmission among family members. First human-to-human transmission reported outside Wuhan.
4 more cases, 3 imported and one transmitted.
13 new cases, 12 of the 53 cases were locally transmitted and 20 cases were foreigners.
5 new cases. 3rd city outside Hubei reaching 100+ cases.
First confirmed case, detected at Incheon International Airport (imported).
Second confirmed case, detected at Incheon Int. Airport. (Transferred to Seoul).
Third confirmed case, according to officials the man engaged in normal activities after flying into Incheon International Airport. (Transferred to Goyang).
First 12 confirmed cases, including 1 doctor and 4 nurses (human-to-human transmission).
Hubei starting to report province-wide cases. (See Hubei Province).
52 new cases reported, largest single day entry besides Wuhan.
58 new cases added, first time with more newly added cases than Wuhan (46). * First 2 deaths.
First confirmed (imported) case. Another one confirmed later.
54 new cases. (doubled). First city with 100+ cases outside Hubei.
* First case in Xi'an, Shaanxi infected in Hangzhou by infected patient. Locally transmitted.
15 more cases. Cases doubled. One case from Xi'an, Shaanxi infected here.
Confirmed case in Rushan City, Shandong had contact with case in Zhoushan. Locally transmitted.
2 more cases. Added 12 cases from previous update. Total of 20 cases (red).
Two more cases, railway workers colleagues of 2nd case. * One more case. * One more case.
One more case, locally transmitted by 3rd case.
One confirmed case. First confirmed case moved to Qingdao number due to officially being counted there.
One new case in Donggang District.
First US case and first case outside Asia on a Snohomish County man who returned from Wuhan, treated at Everett hospital.
First confirmed case (imported - transferred to Zhengzhou)
* Tongren, Guizhou first case infected in Changsha at a restaurant. Locally transmitted.
First confirmed case in Yunnan province (imported).
One new case. Adding one more from previous update.
2 more cases. * One case removed to reflect newest update.
First confirmed case of a Thai national that traveled to Wuhan. Third one in the country.
First confirmed case (Imported) and first case in Liaoning province.
First confirmed case and first confirmed case in Anhui province. (Imported)
First confirmed case (imported). Second case confirmed a coronavirus, waiting for further info.
One more case. * 2 more cases, a previous case was transmitted by family member, unclear where.
First 2 confirmed cases in Hainan province (imported).
First 3 confirmed cases, 2 imported ones and one transmitted.
First 2 confirmed cases (imported). Arrived from Chengdu.
First confirmed case and first case in Shanxi (imported). Transferred to Shijiazhuang (Hubei) and later transferred back to Taiyuan.
First case in Ningxia Hui Autonomous Region (imported).
First confirmed case in Guangxi Zhuang Autonomous Region (imported).
* Two more confirmed cases confirmed, imported.
Case from Mianchi County counted in Sanmenxia.
First confirmed case in Hebei province, imported.
First confirmed case in Jiangsu province, imported.
First confirmed case in Heilongjiang province, imported.
First 2 confirmed cases in the city.
Moving first Rizhao case due to officially being counted in Qingdao (transferred).
First confirmed case in Jilin province.
Two more cases, 1 from Luoyang and 1 from Anxi.

* 1 case from Fushun transferred. Counted here.

7 more cases. City on lockdown. * 13 more cases.
2 more cases. * City on lockdown * 2 new cases.
First confirmed case, imported. 1 case transferred from Lianjiang.
First confirmed case in Shaanxi province, imported. From Xi'an.
One more case in Wugong County. Another case from Qianxian County.
First confirmed case, infected by a Wuhan patient in Hangzhou, Zhejiang.
Four more cases, two locally transmitted, one infected in Hangzhou.
First confirmed case in Singapore, imported.
First confirmed case in Gansu province. Patient had a history of travel to Hunan and Jiangxi provinces.
First confirmed case resulting in death outside Wuhan and outside Hubei province. 80-year-old from Nanpi County (Cangzhou).
Partial lockdown, closure of railway system.
First 5 confirmed cases and one death.
Japan confirms a 2nd case on a Wuhan male visiting Tokyo.
3 new cases from chartered flight that arrived from Wuhan. 2 of them asymptomatic.
Confirmed case detected at Incheon Int. Airport being treated in Euljiro (transferred).

First confirmed case. (Plus confirmed case from Rushan transferred here).
First two confirmed cases. 1 other case transferred from Yuanyang County.
First confirmed case that resulted in death.
First 22 confirmed cases, making it the city with highest number of cases reported in a single day outside Wuhan.
45 new cases and 1 death. Updating city to lockdown.

First confirmed case resulting in death.
First confirmed case in the province, imported.
Two new cases. * One new case.
10 new cases. 23 total and 2 first deaths.
Two more cases from Baihe county.
Four more cases. 2 in Xunyang county, 1 in Baihe county and 1 in Ziyang county.
First confirmed case in a male discharged from a Teku hospital, officials trying to locate the person.
First confirmed case and second case in the U.S.
First confirmed case from a man of Jinghong.
First confirmed case, transferred to Ninglang county.
First confirmed case in France and Europe.

* Case from Dongxian officially counted here.
2 more cases, 1 in Ningjin County and one in Leling County.
2 more cases, one in Dongchangfu District and one in Shenxian County.
Second confirmed case. In partial lockdown.
First confirmed case. Added 3 more from previous update.
* One more case in a Chinese national that travelled by bus from Singapore with 17 other people, including wife and child. All of them treated at Selangor hospital.

First 3 confirmed cases from Longwen, Xiangcheng and Zhao'an.

2 more cases, related to previous cases. Locally transmitted.
First confirmed case. Case from Xiandong officially counted here.
First confirmed case in Canada, 3rd confirmed case in North America.

6 new cases of Chinese nationals, being treated in Nonthaburi.

First confirmed case in British Columbia and third case in Canada.
First 4 confirmed cases in the UAE and the Middle East. Cases are all from a Chinese family. Location not 100% certain, waiting for further details from the UAE government.
First confirmed case in the state and 7th in Australia.
